{"id":166928,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/07/广西警方把奔驰伪装成本田/","date":"2011-07-12T20:00:03Z","modified":"2011-07-12T20:00:03Z","title":"广西警方把奔驰伪装成本田","content":"<p>也许曾有段时间，中国居民分辨不清什么是奔驰什么是本田；如今中国已跻身汽车销量第一大国，应该不会张冠李戴了。然而，警方没有与时俱进：广西防城港东兴市警方将价格百万以上的奔驰车伪装成价值二十万的本田车。 警车前后所挂车标均为“本田”，车尾还有型号“CR-V”标识，但是外形还是奔驰的外形，是奔驰ML350伪装而成。防城港市公安局称，该车为被查扣的无主车，后“为了工作”被东兴市公安局交管大队喷涂为警车，但“没有改装，也没有使用过”。<img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://solidot.org.feedsportal.com/c/33236/f/556826/s/16985fd4/mf.gif\" border=\"0\" /></p>\n<div>\n<table border=\"0\">\n<tr>\n<td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://res.feedsportal.com/viral/sendemail2.html?title=%E5%B9%BF%E8%A5%BF%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E6%8A%8A%E5%A5%94%E9%A9%B0%E4%BC%AA%E8%A3%85%E6%88%90%E6%9C%AC%E7%94%B0&#038;link=http%3A%2F%2Fhardware.solidot.org%2Farticle.pl%3Fsid%3D11%2F07%2F12%2F0656256%26amp%3Bfrom%3Drss\"><img src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/images/emailthis2.gif\" border=\"0\" /></a></td>\n<td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://res.feedsportal.com/viral/bookmark.cfm?title=%E5%B9%BF%E8%A5%BF%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E6%8A%8A%E5%A5%94%E9%A9%B0%E4%BC%AA%E8%A3%85%E6%88%90%E6%9C%AC%E7%94%B0&#038;link=http%3A%2F%2Fhardware.solidot.org%2Farticle.pl%3Fsid%3D11%2F07%2F12%2F0656256%26amp%3Bfrom%3Drss\"><img src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/images/bookmark.gif\" border=\"0\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/106217376903/u/49/f/556826/c/33236/s/16985fd4/a2.htm\"><img src=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/106217376903/u/49/f/556826/c/33236/s/16985fd4/a2.img\" border=\"0\" /></a></p>\n<div>\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?a=CHDuQwARx_g:VWQm1W-38bU:yIl2AUoC8zA\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?d=yIl2AUoC8zA\" border=\"0\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?a=CHDuQwARx_g:VWQm1W-38bU:7Q72WNTAKBA\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?d=7Q72WNTAKBA\" border=\"0\" /></a>\n</div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</